      "dct:title": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Development of educational qualifications at secondary schools in the canton of Thurgau from 2000"
      },
      "dct:description": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Development of educational qualifications at secondary schools and vocational secondary schools in the canton of Thurgau by type of secondary school since the calendar year 2000. The data are differentiated by year and degree type. The number of degrees at secondary schools in the canton of Thurgau is shown. The data are collected as part of the statistics of educational qualifications for the Federal Statistical Office. This is a full survey. Data are collected annually in January/February."
      },
